title: Afraid to take the Before Pic? Here's some motivation.
itunes:title: Afraid to take the Before Pic? Here's some motivation.
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

Today I talk about the before picture. It can be scary. But most of us think it's because we don't like what we see. What's really happening is a lack of belief that we will be an after. Learn how to take one, what to start thinking and a special bonus tip on how to get focused on TODAY's small actions making that AFTER photo a reality.
